#. type: Plain text
#: _versions/3.34/guides/getting-started-testing.adoc
msgid "Building on the features provided by `QuarkusMock`, Quarkus also allows users to effortlessly take advantage of link:https://site.mockito.org/[Mockito] for mocking the beans supported by `QuarkusMock`."
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: _versions/3.34/guides/getting-started-testing.adoc
msgid "This functionality is available with the `@io.quarkus.test.InjectMock` annotation **only if** the `quarkus-junit-mockito` dependency is present:"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: _versions/3.34/guides/getting-started-testing.adoc
